title: Hyperion Looking for Top D3 + to qualify for ESL Meisterschaft
body:
Hello,

We are looking for a top team to qualify for the ESL Meisterschaft. You want to be from Germany, Austria, Switzerland, Liechtenstein and Luxembourg. Be 16 yrs + and be D3 + in SoloQ.

If you are interested in having a tryout, please either add me in game or post on the thread below.

Thanks, 
IGN: The FreudianSlip
